				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Just released 0.8.1.<br /><br />The main changes are:<br />-Lots of code optimizations that make Mesen 15-35% faster (depends on game) than before. This makes it more or less even with FCEUX when using the &quot;New PPU&quot; option (overall, some games are faster in Mesen, others faster in FCEUX).<br />-Audio equalizer (no presets available just yet)<br />-PAL/MMC5/FDS emulation accuracy fixes<br />-Support for UPS/BPS patch files<br />-Option to enable OAM RAM decay emulation (decays to $FF after 3000 cpu cycles with no read/write access, roughly 1.7ms)</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

