						<div class="postbody">It was a simple fix in the end, I just replaced the ratios I was using with the ones you gave me.  2x NTSC now outputs 585x480 and 2x PAL is 709x480.<br />With that, the circles in the 240p test rom are perfectly circular - looks a lot better than the older ratios. :)<br /><br />Thanks for letting me know about this!</div>

